Title Review: No data analysis The application starts to analyze data only from the moment it is installed! That is  it cannot pick up geolocation data from the phone for the previous period. Established with the whole family and everyone was upset that we could not find out if they had been in contact until now. And on TV  the announcement was precisely with an emphasis on previous contacts.
